pageProduct.name: Voost Vitamin B+ Performance Effervescent 60 Pack
pageProduct.description:
General Information

VÖOST Vitamin B+ Performance Orange Helps Maintain General Health & Wellbeing

VÖOST the great tasting vitamin BOOST

We're passionate about all things effervescent and we're on a mission to make vitamin supplements a bit more appealing! We're armed with the world's largest range of effervescent vitamins and minerals to help you find just the right one to suit your needs.

Simple to use. Premium formulation. Great tasting. Effervescent Vitamins and Minerals

Suitable For: Vegan Friendly

Lifestyle Claim: Vegan

Size: 60 Tablets

Flavour: Orange

Serving Size: 1 Tablet

Servings Per Pack: 60

KEY FEATURES

• VÖOST Vitamin B+ Performance Orange Helps Support Energy Production
• VÖOST Vitamin B+ Performance Orange Helps Support Energy Production
• VÖOST Vitamin B+ Performance Orange Helps Support Energy Production
• VÖOST Vitamin B+ Performance Orange Helps Support Energy Production

Warnings

ALWAYS READ THE LABEL. FOLLOW THE DIRECTIONS FOR USE.
Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Adults only. Keep out of reach of children. Store tube tightly closed in a cool, dry place. Store below 25°C. Do not use if tamper evident seal is broken or missing. Contains Sucralose.

IMPORTANT INFORMATION

No added dairy, lactose, soy or yeast.

Ingredients

Thiamine (Vit B1) (as Thiamine Hydrochloride) 20 mg
Riboflavin (Vit B2) (as Riboflavin Sodium Phosphate) 20 mg
Nicotinamide (Vit B3) 50 mg
Pantothenic Acid (Vit B5) (as Calcium Pantothenate) 25 mg
Pyridoxine (Vit B6) (as Pyridoxine Hydrochloride) 10 mg
Cyanocobalamin (Vit B12) 10 microgram
Ascorbic Acid (Vit C) 500 mg
Biotin 150 microgram
Folic Acid 400 microgram
Magnesium (as Magnesium Oxide and Magnesium Carbonate Hydrate) 105 mg
Calcium (as Calcium Carbonate) 100 mg
Zinc (as Zinc Sulfate Monohydrate) 10 mg
Each tablet contains 120 mg of sodium

Contains: Each tablet contains 120 mg of sodium

Directions

Adults: Take 1 tablet daily, dissolved in 200 ml of water, or as directed by your health professional.

USAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Adults: Take 1 tablet daily, dissolved in 200mL of water, or as directed by your healthcare professional.

Start with 200mL of fresh water.
Add one VOOST tablet & watch it fizz.
Once dissolved, it's ready to drink!
Experience the fizz!

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store tube tightly closed in a cool, dry place. Store below 25°C. Do not use if tamper evident seal is broken or missing.

Storage Temperature: Below 25°C.

RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

Please recycle this box.

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
